Modifications and Derivative Works by Michael R. Mull / Lazarus Systems:

  The following components are original works created by Lazarus Systems and
  constitute Derivative Works under the Apache License 2.0:

  1. COBOL-to-C++17 Transpilation (programs/)
     - All 44 _hardened.cpp files are the output of the Lazarus transpiler
       applied to the original AWS CardDemo COBOL source code
     - Includes security hardening: FixedString<N>, SafeInt<T>, Decimal,
       bounds checking, input validation, and RAII memory safety

  2. C++17 CICS Runtime Library (cobol-runtime/)
     - Complete CICS runtime implementation in C++17
     - VSAM storage engine (SQLite-backed KSDS/RRDS/ESDS)
     - BMS screen engine (field attributes, AID keys, map/mapset registry)
     - CICS context (25+ CICS operations: file I/O, TSQ/TDQ, program control)
     - SQL context (SQLite execution, cursor lifecycle, host variable substitution)
     - Transaction loop (session management, TRANSID routing, dispatch)
     - Web server (HTTP REST API for 3270 terminal emulation)
     - 189 tests (107 unit + 82 integration), 476 assertions

  3. React 3270 Terminal UI (carddemo-ui/)
     - Web-based 3270 terminal emulator
     - React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
     - Field-level input, cursor navigation, AID key support

  4. Build System (CMakeLists.txt)
     - CMake build configuration for library, executable, and tests

  5. Program Registry and Integration (programs/main.cpp, program_registry.cpp)
     - Runtime initialization, VSAM file registration, TRANSID mapping
     - CardDemo SQL schema and seed data

